text:
My favorite place to buy Indonesian groceries. Even though the price is a lot more expensive compared to buying at Indonesia but it is way more convenient to buy here.

It is located at level 3 lucky plaza. It accepts paynow as payment.

Very friendly store attendant, speak bahasa as well.
Feel like i shop in Indonesia warung :) wide variety of Indo goods & im obsessed. The lady that works there very friendly. Thank you

Honestly the most elaborate shop in Singapore which sells Indonesian foods, snacks, ingredients, all very specific Indonesian stuffs, just like Warung concept in Indo. Prices are very much reasonable. I love Waroeng Indo.

Recently found this place in Lucky Plaza. I am surprised to see this small store has a lot of varieties on Indonesia's food and other stuffs. To my surprise, they even sell Kecap Bango, Minyak Kayu Putih Cap Ayam and the Saltcheese biscuit. Definitely will be a store where I hunt my craving for Indonesia's food.
very good and nice environment, amazing friendly staffs. mak lurve
